{"tid":2332722,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港電台：印度新型肺炎確診個案突破1千萬宗","createTime":"2020-12-19T22:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T22:49:09.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a2dafb4b488c680af2106f96d8ad7703a3b66d15","tid":2332722,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T22:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566179-20201219.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566179-20201219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWKjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=29afa801\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566179-20201219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=bbb70c04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566179-20201219.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n印度的新型肺炎確診個案，<strong>突破1千萬宗，成為繼美國之後，第二個確診個案超過1千萬宗的國家。美國現時累計1745萬宗確診。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>印度過去一日新增2萬7千多宗病例，累計14萬5千多人死亡。</strong>當地傳媒報道，印度確診個案的增幅逐步放緩，意味疫情正逐步好轉。報道又表示，目前有三家公司正向印度政府申請新冠疫苗緊急使用權，其中包括輝瑞疫苗，當局正審核申請。"},{"pid":"6468fbb30a98edbd6c4e0e8a3af7845e9556515e","tid":2332722,"uid":170772,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T22:44:24.000Z","msg":"客觀陳述數據 都俾你屈做鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想連登仔唔鬥黃仲難過香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc41b2ca0af754763ae49605b3f380179da46cda","tid":2332722,"uid":5065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6468fbb30a98edbd6c4e0e8a3af7845e9556515e","tid":2332722,"uid":170772,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T22:44:24.000Z","msg":"客觀陳述數據 都俾你屈做鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想連登仔唔鬥黃仲難過香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\